Step 1:
======
-> Copy the data from local to HDFS using the following commands
	
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive/json
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive/json/task1

	hadoop fs -put /home/orinit/Desktop/hive_tasks/files/student1.json /hive/json/task1/student1.json

	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive/xml
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive/xml/task1

	hadoop fs -put /home/orinit/Desktop/hive_tasks/files/student1.xml /hive/xml/task1/student1.xml

Note: '/home/orinit/Desktop/hive_tasks/files/student1.json', '/home/orinit/Desktop/hive_tasks/files/student1.xml' both are my local path
-----


-> create a database as 'taskone';

	CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS taskone;


